data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxurious 55+ living in the Four Seasons community! Nestled against a backdrop of towering trees, this expansive Capitiva Model stands as one of the largest models, offering unparalleled privacy. As you approach, the grandeur of the residence becomes evident, with a perfect blend of sophistication and natural beauty.  Upon entering, the home exudes warmth with beautiful hardwood floors that lead you through the formal living and dining rooms. The main level living space is designed to be bathed in natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere that welcomes you home. The kitchen boasts Granite countertops, 42’ cabinets, a tile backsplash, and ceramic flooring and is equipped with modern conveniences, including gas cooking and stainless steel appliances. The adjacent breakfast nook provides a charming space to enjoy your morning tea or coffee.  Connected to the kitchen is a family room featuring a cozy gas fireplace, creating the perfect spot for relaxation. Beyond the family room, discover an additional sunroom area that opens up to a private oasis—an expansive patio surrounded by nature, offering the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings or peaceful moments of solitude.  The main level also accommodates a generously sized office, additional bedroom and bath and the Master Bedroom Suite. The master bath is a retreat in itself, featuring a soaking tub and a separate shower, providing a spa-like experience at the end of each day.  Venture upstairs to find a spacious entertainment area, ideal for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. Complemented by an additional bedroom and full bath, the upper level ensures comfort and convenience for your guests. Noteworthy is the substantial storage space, providing ample room for organization, or consider transforming it into a dedicated craft room or workout space tailored to your preferences. The possibilities are as vast as the space itself, offering versatility to cater to your lifestyle and needs.  The Four Seasons community is renowned for its active and vibrant lifestyle, featuring a spectacular 21,500 sq. ft. clubhouse. Indulge in the indoor and outdoor pools, party the night away in the ballroom, stay fit in the state-of-the-art fitness center, or enjoy friendly games in the billiards and game rooms. The community also offers a cyber café, classrooms, bocce ball, tennis/pickleball courts, a putting green, and scenic walking trails.  Embrace the ultimate 55+ lifestyle at Four Seasons, where every day is an opportunity for relaxation, recreation, and connection in a welcoming and secure gated community. Your dream home awaits—experience the pinnacle of retirement living in this remarkable residence surrounded by nature and luxury.
